
Plugins allow you to connect to other services
Ex.: connect to Azure from Jenkins you need Azure Plugin 

Jenkins UI > manage Jenkins >plugin Manager

Installing plugin after Jenkins deployed
-plugins index - https://plugins.jenkins.io/
some plugins might you restart jenkins instance  - sudo systemctl restart jenkins

builds are just thing thats running you CI/CD pipeline and your build process

to limit access to the user need to install plugin -> role-based authorization strategy (plugin)
after install this pulgin you can create role, give permissions and etc -> https://plugins.jenkins.io/role-strategy/


